data.title: the madison club
data.text:
IN WEDDINGS

Every love story is beautiful but yours should be unique.

From the moment you walk through the front doors, you’ll know you’ve arrived somewhere special.

The Club boasts multiple floors of event spaces, each with their own distinct personality and character- from enchanting elegance to modern sophistication. Let us help you find the perfect space to tell your love story. Visit our weddings page to learn more.

BUSINESS & COMMUNITY LEADERS: There’s a reason the Club has been rated Madison’s Best Place for Business. You’ll have access to Madison’s most successful professionals and to events to further your professional growth.

SOCIALITES: Did someone say social outing? From black tie affairs to VIP seating at Concerts on the Square, one of a kind wine tastings to pop up restaurant nights, we’ll fill your calendar with great events.

FOODIES: We bring you the best food in town by partnering with local farmers and purveyors. And while you’re enjoying your delicious food, pair it with a craft or classic cocktail, we have it all.

WEDDING DREAMERS: We eat, sleep, and breathe weddings which is why we are consistently rated one of the best. Whether you have 50 or 200 guests, our expert planners will help you create your perfect day.

LIFE PLANNERS: You love to celebrate milestones?! So do we! From baby showers to Bar Mitzvah’s, epic game nights to grand proposals, birthday parties to retirement farewell, we’re there for all of your milestones.

MEETING MANIA: Meetings are a must, but the chaos of planning is not. Leave it to the experts. From knowing your favorite room to the food you ordered at your last meeting, we have you covered.

FAMILY FUN: Need a date night but can’t find a sitter? No worries, we offer Friday night babysitting, as well as kids’ events, holiday brunches, activities and much more.

RETIREES: Good news; our dining rooms are quiet, we know your favorite table, and your drink is always made just how you like it.

TRAVELERS & RECREATIONALISTS: You said you like to travel? You like golfing even more? Whether you’re hitting the runway or the fairway, we have stays and rounds of golf at Private Clubs across the country.

CITY GURUS: From rooftop lovers to do-gooders, you’ll have the best seats to everything downtown as well as access to the best community focused individuals to join efforts and support the city.

AVID LEARNERS: For our learners - we have you covered with WisPolitics, group cooking classes, and Lunch & Learns. Expand your knowledge from the kitchen to the meeting room.

EVERYONE & ANYONE: We welcome members who will revel in our old traditions and introduce a few new ones of their own. Ignore the stigmas of a social club, and experience life at the Madison Club.
